channel.title: Moving home, tele commands etc
channel.description:
Well as you know, You have the basic mage menu, with the tele tabs, going to like, jad cave, minigames etc..
I just want to know how to change the name of a teleport, and where it teleports you to.
And how to move npc's, liek to make a new home area.

item.title: Moving home, tele commands etc
item.dc:creator: @Scape-JAVA Scape-JAVA
item.description:
@Scape-JAVA wrote:

For the tele command, go into clickingmost.java

and then find w.e

and then something like this.

// lumbridge teleport c.triggerTele(3222, 3218, 0); break;
